                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/385847bdc2e3a8c4764a12bef5aaa654_821551799796196441.mp3"
                  },
                  {
