                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/80548ece239d50364a57570309eb0fbd_8338159905545030528.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations75241",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/006b24bb4d16eb5e63105de1b4bb8347_3364938264399342462.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p>Le manteau appartement à Halsey, la dame qui a disparu, a été retrouvé dans le tunnel. La raison reste inconnue.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Paimon : Je n&#39;arrive pas à comprendre ! Réfléchis-y aussi, Voyageur/euse.</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/11/29705491/3776aa5a338f1d01d510b6ffeea2532f_5637539089517347717.png",
                "title": "Preuve pertinente - Tunnel : Vêtements de femme"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations31238",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/4f5b5fc0abcf76cf9a29b0607f2a5510_1820573591993735082.mp3"
