                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations80832",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/bd9123f98d05dd0605ba07eefd54c5bc_223127285548352171.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations16237",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/9954eb7f63165a12037fb7f43555a1cd_4792738296793686266.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations26493",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/8817fc73d47d41a937831ce8dd13e736_7705609424464532168.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p>Le défunt est l&#39;un des assistants de Lyney, nommé Cowell. Il avait la confiance de tous ses collègues. Son travail consistait à installer et à inspecter les accessoires, ainsi qu&#39;à aider pendant le spectacle et à garder la foule engagée.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Paimon : Pourquoi ce serait lui ? Étrange...</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/11/29705491/d42ae996472c6916d6d50a0ecc64e960_4956267084063137903.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Opéra : Informations sur l'identité de la victime"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations69852",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/fa1b29255fe4a02ea19fa2099d8bfa19_4643971685173742482.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations86198",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/f9eeaa3df27ec9b158d81a38a235a01b_2391151462524440826.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations20031",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/08029098cd5f84b9d2b34f69aa659452_409923802236656745.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations23239",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/1dc95cbd823456b96516ed8498f16827_2186694336931373888.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p>Halsey est la personne disparue. Peintre assez célèbre, elle est venue assister au spectacle de magie afin d&#39;échapper à la pression de son travail. Aucun lien n&#39;a été découvert entre elle et les membres de la troupe de Lyney.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Paimon : Les disparitions des jeunes femmes étaient-elles toutes aussi difficiles à résoudre ?</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/11/29705491/b4259743d2c447c4d82af4a1f31a4501_6864511355972881193.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Opéra : Informations sur l'identité de la femme disparue"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations97219",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/ee11ea6623ac6416734537a610bc4a43_1580896190321201305.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations56995",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/7383e79c2d4030a020687ee881057e22_480217220092766268.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations98398",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/8630c16157b451ec22a221565f213f19_6583947472305784149.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations87874",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/fbf32278a1e92b6a3a1ad0825c5da5b5_6384911510677430996.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p>Pendant le tour de transposition, de nombreux membres du public ont entendu un bruit sourd.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Paimon : On a tous entendu ce bruit, pas vrai ?</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/11/29705491/101ac81522b15864a2e44ff15d6c762a_2331997717598891373.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Opéra : Bruit étrange pendant le spectacle"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations71658",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/a96cb8b554f455adf00bf0e13a1857fc_5816641961619571086.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations78702",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/32b5f240566f987f81e1e0f19e649570_3813851334627321134.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations25620",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/fa90af6337e46123e7f19e5ababce8c3_1266507271130415302.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations78812",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/6b04528113f7bdf8c215208335ee7314_5731444548033966196.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p>Personne n&#39;a quitté l&#39;Opéra pendant le spectacle de magie, et après l&#39;incident, seuls ceux dont l&#39;identité a été vérifiée par les Gendarmes ont pu sortir.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Paimon : La représentation n&#39;était pas visible depuis le poste du garde. À sa place, je me serais faufilée dans les tribunes.</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/11/29705491/ffa9d5d54dbd875552a7676637228a52_7705083014973277107.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Opéra : Accès de l'Opéra"
              },
              {
                "audios": [
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations35053",
                    "name": "CN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/dcfe75e73065480175b2c857c83e7eb0_4074324447831171876.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations66094",
                    "name": "EN",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/70be4b8c9826081cf6cead1a2fffb6e8_676961063509142344.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations54606",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/71fdfd414ffa7335b3379aa7c2bab9e8_7326385285579183243.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations51511",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/91954def66e9dff883383b1ea62c16ff_6582135183189142924.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p>La boîte magique au centre des tribunes a un double fond, et en dessous se trouve une entrée vers un tunnel souterrain. C&#39;est ainsi que le spectateur chanceux était censé avoir été transporté sans que le public ne s&#39;en aperçoive.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Paimon : Je n&#39;aurais jamais cru que la boîte avait un double fond...</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/11/29705491/a9fff172ef51f51767490d870c8ccbb7_9088561688115640232.png",
                "title": "Indice pertinent - Opéra : Boîte magique du côté du public"
              },
              {
