                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations81762",
                    "name": "JP",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/711dcd7e2c8183217bfd5b9c9ac31b1a_909662546187061546.mp3"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "Autres informations63580",
                    "name": "KR",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki-voice/2024/02/11/29705491/7fe1f9ae91ce8df7b0c2f9a0514f48c5_8047551533628423699.mp3"
                  }
                ],
                "desc": "<p>Le liquide que les Gendarmes ont trouvé dans les affaires de Cowell semble avoir la capacité de dissoudre les Fontainois dans l&#39;eau...</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">Paimon : Je n&#39;arrive pas à croire que les gens peuvent vraiment se transformer en eau...</span></p>",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/11/29705491/658c12ca4a0d2bd799a42bad8bf29fc4_3876451873391192997.png",
